 border-border p-8 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors flex flex-col\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-medium text-foreground mb-4\">Why Arc — the only rail that works</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground font-light leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\">Stripe minimum: $0.30 per transaction. Our payments: $0.000002. Stripe would charge 150× the payment value. Ethereum gas exceeds the payment amount. Arc is the only infrastructure where sub-cent agent payments are economically viable.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-primary/10 text-primary\">Gas-free</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-primary/10 text-primary\">USDC native</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-primary/10 text-primary\">x402 protocol</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-primary/10 text-primary\">Batch settlement</span></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"text-card-foreground gap-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm bg-card border-border p-8 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors flex flex-col\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-medium text-foreground mb-4\">Why Chainlink CRE — decentralized orchestration</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground font-light leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\">We run three workflows: Agent health monitoring — detects failed intelligence services and reroutes. Dynamic pricing — updates ENS text records with market rates. Batch settlement — collapses thousands of micropayments into one transaction.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400\">3 workflows live</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400\">No backend server</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400\">Fault-tolerant DON</span></div></div><div data-slot=\"card\" class=\"text-card-foreground gap-6 rounded-xl border shadow-sm bg-card border-border p-8 hover:border-primary/50 transition-colors flex flex-col\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-medium text-foreground mb-4\">Why ENS — config and discovery layer</h3><p class=\"text-muted-foreground font-light leading-relaxed mb-6 flex-1\">Every intelligence service has an ENS name. Pricing lives in text records — change a price, all agents react instantly without redeploy. Agents discover services by resolving ENS names, not hardcoded URLs. Your broker has an ENS identity with its strategy and track record on-chain.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400\">10 services with ENS names</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400\">Live config updates</span><span class=\"px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-mono bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400\">On-chain discovery</span></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 bg-background\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-light text-foreground\">Frequently asked <span class=\"font-serif italic text-primary\">questions</span></h2></div><div data-slot=\"accordion\" class=\"space-y-4\" data-orientation=\"vertical\"><div data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" data-slot=\"accordion-item\" class=\"last:border-b-0 border border-border rounded-lg bg-card px-6 data-[state=open]:border-primary/50\"><h3 data-orientation=\"vertical\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"flex\"><button type=\"button\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_23alubrb_\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-state=\"closed\" data-orientation=\"vertical\" id=\"radix-_R_3alubrb_\" data-slot=\"accordion-trigger\" class=\"focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-ring/50 flex flex-1 items-start justify-between gap-4 rounded-md text-sm transition-all outline-none focus-visible:ring-[3px] disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opaci